/li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/MSGestureStart_event\"><code>MSGestureStart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/MSGestureTap_event\"><code>MSGestureTap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/MSInertiaStart_event\"><code>MSInertiaStart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/MSManipulationStateChanged_event\"><code>MSManipulationStateChanged</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/paste_event\"><code>paste</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/pointercancel_event\"><code>pointercancel</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/pointerdown_event\"><code>pointerdown</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/pointerenter_event\"><code>pointerenter</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/pointerleave_event\"><code>pointerleave</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/pointermove_event\"><code>pointermove</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/pointerout_event\"><code>pointerout</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/pointerover_event\"><code>pointerover</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/pointerup_event\"><code>pointerup</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/scroll_event\"><code>scroll</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/securitypolicyviolation_event\"><code>securitypolicyviolation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/show_event\"><code>show</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/touchcancel_event\"><code>touchcancel</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/touchend_event\"><code>touchend</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/touchmove_event\"><code>touchmove</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/touchstart_event\"><code>touchstart</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/transitioncancel_event\"><code>transitioncancel</code></a></li><li><em><code>transitionend</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/transitionrun_event\"><code>transitionrun</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/transitionstart_event\"><code>transitionstart</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforcechanged_event\"><code>webkitmouseforcechanged</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforcedown_event\"><code>webkitmouseforcedown</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforceup_event\"><code>webkitmouseforceup</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforcewillbegin_event\"><code>webkitmouseforcewillbegin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/wheel_event\"><code>wheel</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><code>transitionend</code>&nbsp;事件会在 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Transitions/Using_CSS_transitions\">CSS transition</a>&nbsp;结束后触发。当 transition 完成前移除 transition 时，比如移除 css 的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/transition-property\"><code>transition-property</code></a> 属性，事件将不会被触发。如在 transition 完成前设置&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/display\"><code>display</code></a> 为\"<code>none\"</code>，事件同样不会被触发。</p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">是否冒泡</th>\n   <td>是</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">是否可取消</th>\n   <td>是</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">接口</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">事件处理器属性</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/transitionend_event\" title=\"ontransitionend\"><code>ontransitionend</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p><code>transitionend</code> 事件是双向触发的 - 当完成到转换状态的过渡，以及完全恢复到默认或非转换状态时都会触发。&nbsp;如果没有过渡延迟或持续时间，即两者的值都为 0s 或者都未声明，&nbsp;则不发生过渡，并且任何过渡事件都不会触发。如果触发了&nbsp;<code>transitioncancel</code>&nbsp;事件，则<code>transitionend</code>&nbsp;事件不会触发。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/*\n * 在指定的元素上监听 transitionend 事件，例如#slidingMenu\n * 然后指定一个函数，例如 showMessage()\n */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">showMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Transition 已完成'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> element <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"slidingMenu\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nelement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"transitionend\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> showMessage<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"{{Specifications}}"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLElement.transitionend_event","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Element/transitionend_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参考","title":"参考","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>The <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code></a> interface and the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/transitionend_event\" title=\"The 'transitionend' event\"><code>transitionend</code></a> event.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/transition\"><code>transition</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/transition-delay\"><code>transition-delay</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/transition-duration\"><code>transition-duration</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/transition-property\"><code>transition-property</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/transition-timing-function\"><code>transition-timing-function</code></a>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参考","id":"参考"}],"summary":"transitionend 事件会在 CSS transition 结束后触发。当 transition 完成前移除 transition 时，比如移除 css 的transition-property 属性，事件将不会被触发。如在 transition 完成前设置  display 为\"none\"，事件同样不会被触发。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"transitionend","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.ontransitionend","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/element/transitionend_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/element/transitionend_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API","title":"指数"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Element/transitionend_event","title":"transitionend"}],"pageTitle":"transitionend | MDN","noIndexing":true}}